name: Unpainted TAM Airlines 777-300ER RTO and Takeoff at Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
Hey everyone, in today's video we have a TAM Airlines 777-300ER doing a Rejected Take-Off test (RTO), and then departing Paine Field, possibly to get painted. This was one of my first Paine Field videos, so the filming isn't as good. I hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
